| - `Hiding latex meta                              | files <[[https://texblog.org/2015/08/20/hiding-latex-metafiles-from-project-directory/]]>`_       |
|                                                   |                                                                                                   |
| Makefile dan Docker                               |                                                                                                   |
| --------------                                    | --------------                                                                                    |
|                                                   |                                                                                                   |
| Simple command:                                   |                                                                                                   |
|                                                   |                                                                                                   |
| #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE                                   |                                                                                                   |
|     compile:                                      |                                                                                                   |
| #+END_EXAMPLE                                     |                                                                                                   |
| #+BEGIN_QUOTE                                     | -rm -v $(shell pwd):/workdir -w /workdir aergus/latex pdflatex -output-directory=build main.tex   |
|   docker run -                                    |                                                                                                   |
| #+END_QUOTE                                       |                                                                                                   |
|                                                   |                                                                                                   |
| Pilihan image:                                    |                                                                                                   |
|                                                   |                                                                                                   |
| - aergus/latex                                    |                                                                                                   |
| - tianon/latex                                    |                                                                                                   |
|                                                   |                                                                                                   |
